body.description: Color: Black 2 Pack [MFi Certified] USB C Car Charger Fast Charging, 40W Dual Port USB C iPhone Car Charger Adapter with USB C to USB C Cable. Car Charger USB C Specifications: Input Voltage: DC12-24V USB C PD 1 Output: 5V/3A, 9V/2.22A, 12V/1.67A USB C PD 2 Output: 5V/3A, 9V/2.22A, 12V/1.67A Total Output: 40W Max Universal Compatibility For iPhone/iPad iPhone 15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max iPad Pro 12.9 5th/4th/3rd Generation 2021/2020/2018 iPad Pro 11 3rd/2nd/1st Generation 2021/2020/2018 iPad Air 4th Generation 2020 iPad mini 6th Generation 2021 For Android Phones Galaxy S23/S22/S21/S20/S10/S9/Note 20/10 Series And more USB C devices. 4X Faster Charging Speed iPhone 15 fast car charger supports full-speed fast charging of two devices. Fast charging your iPhone 15 Pro Max up to 60% in 30mins. Safe and Fast Charging Multiple protections against over-current, overcharging, and overheating to ensure the safety of your devices. Charging will be automatically stopped when the battery is full. Compact and Durable Lightweight and highly portable, the tiny thumb-sized body fits most car cigarette lighters and barely protrudes past the edge of the outlet, providing a trim, less cluttered look. Blue LED Indicator With the user-friendly specifical design, soft blue LED indicator which is completely non-glaring helps locate the USB ports when charging in the dark. MFi Certified USB C to USB C Cable Built with MFi certified chip, build double protection for your devices. The 3.3ft iPhone 15 charger cable length allows you to charge your devices from an extra-long distance. What You Get 2 * 40W Dual USB C Car Charger 2 * 3.3FT MFi Certified USB C to USB C Cable A 3-Year Warranty and 24/7 Friendly Customer Service.
